Save Search

Save a Search

To save a search:

  1. Open the search form. You can use basic search or advanced search
  2. Enter the search criteria
  3. Execute the search
  4. The search result will be displayed
  5. Name the search and click Save

The system opens a confirmation message. Confirm by clicking on the Create New button. The saved searches are visible on the users dashboard.

Open Saved Search

Open saved search from filter in basic and advanced search form

You can open and load existing saved searches in the search form and can run it again. To open the search preset:

  1. Select the saved search button
  2. Select the search from the list with all saved searches is displayed
  3. You can use the auto-suggest option easily to find the search name

The saved searches can be found on the users dashboard
